        'Redirect\x20to\x20Start',
        'Session\x20Snapshot\x20Restore',
        'APM\x20Master\x20keeps\x20track\x20of\x20your\x20place\x20as\x20you\x20work\x20—\x20the\x20screen\x20you\x27re\x20on,\x20the\x20record\x20you\x20have\x20open,\x20your\x20search\x20filters,\x20and\x20even\x20the\x20active\x20tab.\x20If\x20your\x20session\x20expires\x20or\x20the\x20page\x20reloads,\x20a\x20restore\x20prompt\x20slides\x20in\x20offering\x20to\x20take\x20you\x20right\x20back\x20where\x20you\x20were.',
        'relative',
        'var(--apm-accent,\x20#3498db)',
        'Restore',
        'When\x20a\x20search\x20or\x20navigation\x20results\x20in\x20a\x20single\x20work\x20order,\x20it\x20opens\x20automatically\x20—\x20no\x20need\x20to\x20click\x20the\x20row.\x20Works\x20for\x20links\x20opened\x20in\x20new\x20tabs,\x20same-tab\x20searches,\x20and\x20forecast\x20results.',
