        '600',
        'AutoFill\x20Profiles',
        'A\x20New\x20Record\x20Template\x20—\x20the\x20checkbox\x20is\x20checked,\x20so\x20this\x20profile\x20is\x20offered\x20on\x20brand-new\x20work\x20orders\x20without\x20needing\x20a\x20keyword\x20match.',
        'Open\x20the\x20',
        'New\x20Record\x20Template:\x20',
        'Multi-Screen\x20Support:\x20',
        'The\x20teal\x20Auto\x20Fill\x20button\x20appears\x20contextually\x20on\x20matching\x20work\x20orders.',
        'Book\x20labor\x20and\x20track\x20your\x20hours\x20without\x20navigating\x20away\x20from\x20the\x20work\x20order.',
